OL,3,CChannel 4 removes all seasons of MAFS
OL,4,CUK after rape allegations
OL,6,FChannel 4 has removed all previous
OL,7,Fseasons of Married At First Sight UK
OL,8,Ffrom its platforms after "very serious
OL,9,Fallegations".
OL,11,FThe BBC reported that two women said
OL,12,Fthey were raped by their onscreen
OL,13,Fhusbands, while a third described an
OL,14,Fallegation of a non-consensual sex act.
OL,16,FThe broadcaster said that all previous
OL,17,Fseasons of MAFS UK have been removed
OL,18,Ffrom its streaming and linear
OL,19,Fservices, and it announced that in
OL,20,FApril, it commissioned an external
OL,21,Freview into contributor welfare.
OL,26,@pD@ZOUqD@LO]
