OL,3,CChannel 4 removes all seasons of MAFS
OL,4,CUK after rape allegations
OL,6,F"In April, Channel 4 was presented
OL,7,Fwith serious allegations of wrongdoing
OL,8,Fagainst a small number of past
OL,9,Fcontributors, allegations that we
OL,10,Funderstand those contributors have
OL,11,Fdenied," Channel 4 said in a statement
OL,12,Fon Monday.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
