OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779214266
OL,3,CChannel 4 removes all seasons of MAFS
OL,4,CUK after rape allegations
OL,6,FThe show, which is produced for
OL,7,FChannel 4 by independent production
OL,8,Fcompany CPL, sees single people
OL,9,Fmatched by experts "marry" strangers
OL,10,Fwho they meet for the first time on
OL,11,Ftheir wedding day.
OL,13,FChannel 4 said they believed "that
OL,14,Fwhen concerns related to contributor
OL,15,Fwelfare were raised through existing
OL,16,Fwelfare and production protocols,
OL,17,Fprompt and appropriate action was
OL,18,Ftaken, based on the information
OL,19,Favailable at the time."
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@ZO]
