OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779214266
OL,3,CChannel 4 removes all seasons of MAFS
OL,4,CUK after rape allegations
OL,6,F"Channel 4 strongly refutes any claim
OL,7,Fto the contrary."
OL,9,FPriya Dogra, chief executive of
OL,10,FChannel 4 said: "I want to express my
OL,11,Fsympathy to contributors who have
OL,12,Fclearly been distressed after taking
OL,13,Fpart in Married At First Sight UK.
OL,15,F"The wellbeing of our contributors is
OL,16,Falways of paramount importance."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@QO]rD@QOU
